\c 14
\s Abhuramu anorwira Roti
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika mumazuva aAmuraferi mambo weShinari, Arioki ma­mbo weErasari, Kedhoriraomeri ma­mbo weEramu, naTidhari, mambo wemarudzi,
\v 2 \add kuti\add* vakaita hondo naBhera mambo weSodhoma, naBherisha mambo weGomora, Shinabhi mambo weAdhamu, naShemebheri mambo weZebhoimi, namambo weBhera (rinova Zoari).
\v 3 Ava vose vakasangana mumu­pata weSidhimu unova Gungwa reMunyu.
\v 4 Makore gumi nemaviri vakashandira Kedhoriraomeri, asi vaka\add mu\add*mukira negore regumi nematatu.
\v 5 Zvino mugore regumi nemana Kedhoriraomeri wakauya, nemadzimambo aiva naye, vakarova vaRefaimi paAshitoreti karinaimi, nevaZuzimi paHamu, nevaEmimi paShavhe-kiriataimi,
\v 6 nevaHori pagomo ravo Seiri, kusvi­kira paEriparani riri pedo nerenje.
\v 7 Zvino va­kadzoka vakasvika Enimishipati rinova Kadheshi, ndokurova nyika yose yevaAmareki, nevaAmoriwo, vaigara paHazazoni-Tamari.
\p
\v 8 Zvino kwakabuda mambo weSodhoma nama­mbo weGomora, namambo weAdhamu namambo weZebhoimi, namambo weBhera rinova Zoari, vakabuda vakarongedza hondo kuzorwa navo pamupata weSidhimu,
\v 9 kuti varwe naKedhorirao­meri mambo weEramu, naTidhari, mambo wemarudzi, naAmuraferi mambo weShinari, naArioki, mambo weErasari; madzimambo mana akamirisana nemadzi­mambo mashanu.
\v 10 Zvino mupata weSi­dhimu \add waiva ne\add*makomba ane tara, uye madzimambo eSodhoma neGomora akatiza, ndokuwiramo; uye vakasara vakatizira kugomo,
\v 11 ndokutora nhumbi dzose dzeSo­dhomu neGomora, nechikafu chavo chose, vakaenda.
\v 12 Zvino vakatora Roti, mwanakomana wemunun'una waAbhu­ramu, waigara paSodhoma, nenhumbi dzake, ndokuenda.
\p
\v 13 Zvino kwakauya wakange apuku­nyuka ndokuudza Abhuramu muHebheru, waigara pamiouki* yaMamure muAmori, mu­nun'una waEshikori nemunun'una waAneri vakange vaita sungano naAbhuramu.
\v 14 Zvino Abhuramu wakati anzwa kuti hama yake yatapwa, akashongedza zvombo vakange vadzidziswa, vaka­zvarwa muimba yake, mazana ma­tatu negumi nevasere, aka\add va\add*teverera ku­svikira paDhani.
\v 15 Zvino wakazvikamura kurwa navo usiku, iye nevaranda vake, akavarova, akavateverera kusvikira paHobha, riri kurudyi rweDhamasiko.
\v 16 Zvino wakadzosa nhumbi dzose, naRotiwo hama yake nenhumbi dzake, nevakadziwo neva­nhu.
\v 17 Mambo weSodhoma ndoku­buda kunosangana naye adzoka pakuuraya Kedhoraomari nemadzimambo aiva naye pamupata weShavhe unova mupata wamambo.
\v 18 Merikizedheki mambo weSaremi ndokuuisa chingwa newaini; uye iye mupristi waMwari Wekumusoro-soro.
\p
\v 19 Zvino wakamuropafadza akati: Ngaaropafadzwe Abhuramu naMwari Wekumusoro-soro, Muridzi wematenga nepasi.
\p
\v 20 Uye ngaaropafadzwe Mwari Wekumusoro-soro, wakakumikidza vavengi vako mumaoko ako. Ndokumupa chegumi chezvose.
\p
\v 21 Zvino mambo weSodhoma wakati kuna Abhuramu: Ndipe vanhu, ugozvitorera nhumbi.
\p
\v 22 Abhuramu ndokuti kuna mambo weSodhoma: Ndasimudzira ruoko rwa­ngu kuna Jehovha Mwari Wekumusoro-soro, muridzi wekumatenga nepasi,
\v 23 kuti handingatori kubva kurushinda kusvika kurukanda rwe­shangu pane chose chaunacho, kuti murege kuzoti: Ini ndakafumisa Abhuramu.
\v 24 Kunze kweizvo chete majaya zvaakadya, nemugove wevarume vakainda neni, va­naAneri, Eshikori, naMamure, ngava­tore mugove wavo.
